OL,5, A man has been been sentenced to a     
OL,6, whole-life prison term for murdering   
OL,7, Met Police sergeant Matiu Ratana.      
OL,9,FSgt Ratana, 54, was shot in the chest  
OL,10,Fand leg at Croydon custody centre by   
OL,11,FLouis De Zoysa, who had smuggled an    
OL,12,Fantique gun into the building following
OL,13,Fhis arrest on 25 September 2020.       
OL,15,FHe was found guilty of murder, having  
OL,16,Fclaimed diminished responsibility.     
OL,18,FSgt Ratana's partner Su Bushby said her
OL,19,Fgrief was "tormenting" and spoke of an 
OL,20,F"intense" feeling of emptiness.        
